    <div class="card-body border">
        <p class="card-text text-center">Be the fantasy hero you only dreamed of! This is a Location based game! This means you will interact with our current real world in a new and exciting way! Choose a class, lvl up your hero, learn incredible skills, fight terrible monsters, find loot, take over land, protect it yourself or with the help of your guild, find resources make better equipment, and setup trade routes to find resources. Fight legendary boss creatures on their turf, or protect your own from invasions!</p>
    </div>

</div>
